message.body: Hey! Meeting was weird and a downer (old faculty are real crotchety) but nothing major that will effect us. A few changes allowing 1 person to teach versus co teaching and student caps as well as getting rid of the themes for fall 2015.
I have a meeting from 10-1 at temple tmw but maybe on the way home we can meet up and I can relay more info and give you the agenda that basically covers everything.
I'm so mad I missed the crotchety oldburgers. I love those at meetings. I am around all day tomorrow... Whenever you get a chance us cool.
Hey! About to leave temple in 10. Should be in west philly by 1:30 do you want me to stop by yr place or meet at the greenline? Whatever's easy!
Of shit, I'm so sorry. Phone was on vibrate. Are you home now? Can I just call you?
